{
  "text": "Can you describe what you call the psychic component and tell me why it is strong at this particular time? I am wrong. We shall elect not to retrace the previously given information, but rather elect to note that the psychic attack upon this instrument is at a constant level as long as it continues in this particular surface of variations towards the distortion of intensity of attack occur due to the opportunities represented by the entity in any weakness at this particular nexus. The entity has been dealing with the distortion which you call pain for some time as you call this a measurement. This creates a particularly favorable target of opportunity and the entity of which we have previously spoken has taken this opportunity to attempt to be of service in its own way. It is a fortune it for the ongoing vitality of this contact that the instrument is a strong willed entity with little tendency towards the distortion called among your people's hysteria since the dizzying effects of this attack have been a constant and at times disruptive for several of your diurnal periods. However, this particular entity is adapting well to the situation without undue distortions and towards a fear. Thus the psychic attack is not as successful, but does have some deriging influence upon the instrument.",
